    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i swear im losing my mind lol but i just checked my old backup drive and like half my cloud storage files from 2021 are just... gone? not in trash, just gone. and my linkedin activity is all wiped too. i feel like someone is actually deleting my stuff. has anyone ever heard of companies doing this to specific people?",
