    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i already tried contacting them and the support staff was so weirdly unhelpful. like they kept giving me these \"scripted\" answers about sync errors even though i know for a fact i didn't change my settings. it felt almost like they were being told to avoid the subject. anyone actually believe it's just a \"glitch\" when things only disappear once i start talking about certain topics online?",
